Henry Hugglemonster: Roarsome Tales is a 2014 Disney DVD compilation of five episodes of the new Disney Junior animated series. In the friendly town of Roarsville, each monster is special as the monsterpet they take care of. As Henry Hugglemonster and his friends and family discovers and make friends with various monsterpets and other creatures. The DVD special features include sneak peeks of other Disney favourites, like Sleeping Beauty Special Edition, Aladdin Special Edition, a trailer for DisneyNature's Monkey Kingdom and a special teaser trailer for the live-action adaption of Disney's Cinderella. Henry Hugglemonster: Roarsome Tales is sure to be a favourite with kids and their pets!

This is a new favorite show in our household. It teaches how to treat others, problem solving, as well as manners and the importance of family. The intro song is catchy and the colors are great. I highly recommend this dvd for any Hugglemonster family!
